<body>
<p>Reports incorrect Spring context configurations.</p>
<ul>
  <li>Unresolved files and directories in <code>locations</code> attributes
    and corresponding aliased attributes of <code>@ContextConfiguration</code> meta annotations
  </li>
  <li>Missing default application context file</li>
</ul>

<p>For more information, see <a href=https://docs.spring.io/spring-framework/docs/current/javadoc-api/org/springframework/test/context/ContextConfiguration.html>@ContextConfiguration</a>.</p>

<p><b>Example:</b></p>
<pre><code lang="java">
  @ContextConfiguration(locations = "classpath:META-INF/unknown-context.xml") // reports "Cannot resolve file 'unknown-context.xml'"
  class MyTests {...}
</code></pre>
</body>
